News of Sfiso Ncwane s death sent shockwaves through the nation on Monday. https://twitter.com/Candie_Emz/status/805754178677145600The gospel singer died in a Johannesburg hospital on Monday morning.Drum magazine earlier reported that his sister Gugu confirmed his death but had been too upset to elaborate on the details.RIP Sfiso Ncwane&mdash; Abuti Too Much Sauce (@mphontane) December 5, 2016 Sfiso passed on after an alleged kidney failure. He was rushed to the hospital last night after he complained about kidney problems said Sipho Makhabane speaking on behalf of the singer s family. It has also been reported by Move that the Ku Lungile Baba hit maker was vomiting blood on Sunday night.